window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I was the girl no one looked at twice. Until they saw me.</b><br> <br> My whole life, no one has had my back. My parents are dead, my adoptive mother is a drug addict, and the mean girls on campus mock me for my scars.<br> <br> So when I end up desperate for money and out of options, I agree to sell the one thing I have left: my innocence.<br> <br> On the night I’m meant to give my body to a brutal Russian mobster, three men storm into the room like dark shadows and kill him before he can claim me. When they drag me from the blood-soaked bed, I’m certain they’re going to kill me too.<br> <br> They don’t… but they don’t forget about me, either.<br> <br> These three dangerous brothers will do anything to make sure I keep my mouth shut about what I saw, even if it means stalking my every movement. I’m a loose thread to them—but somehow, I’m becoming more than that too.<br> <br> I’m becoming an obsession.<br> A temptation.<br> A craving.<br> <br> And no matter how much I try to deny the terrifying attraction that pulses between us, I know if I don’t find a way out of this tangled web soon…<br> <br> <b>Their darkness will swallow me up.</b><br> <br> <i>This omnibus contains the complete Filthy Wicked Psychos series, a dark new adult romance. It includes high steam, violence, and foul language.</i><br> <br> <i>BOOKS IN THIS SET:</i><br> <i>Twisted Game</i><br> <i>Beautiful Devils</i><br> <i>Corrupt Vow</i><br> <i>Savage Hearts</i></p>"; 
